15:37.619 --> 15:39.445
I hate this
freaking phone, Bobby.

15:39.501 --> 15:41.109
Lin, we're underground.
You can't blame the phone.

15:41.162 --> 15:42.938
What, do you work
for the phone company now?

15:42.993 --> 15:44.266
Bob's Phone Company?

15:44.315 --> 15:45.898
What, are you
going to beat me up?

15:46.092 --> 15:47.595
