to climb out?

16:48.388 --> 16:49.613
Oh, wait!

16:49.660 --> 16:51.335
Here's a grappling hook!

16:51.389 --> 16:53.690
Oh, and here's an escalator!

16:53.999 --> 16:56.400
- Silly me!
- We're about to die, Louise.

16:56.607 --> 16:58.619
